Company About Us:
J Street organizes pro-Israel, pro-peace, pro-democracy Americans to promote US policies that embody our deeply held Jewish and democratic values and that help secure the State of Israel as a democratic homeland for the Jewish people. J Street believes that only a negotiated resolution agreed to by Israelis and Palestinians can meet the legitimate needs and national aspirations of both peoples.  

Working in the American political system, in the Jewish community, and with others with whom it shares core values, J Street advocates for diplomacy-first American leadership and policies that advance justice, equality, peace, and democracy in Israel, in the wider region, and in the United States as well.  

J Street focuses its work in three main areas:  
1)  advocating and demonstrating support for pro-Israel, pro-peace policies in Congress, the media, and the Jewish community;  
2)  endorsing and raising money for federal candidates who share J Street’s agenda; and  
3)  educating the public and raising awareness of the Israeli-Palestinian conflict and the two-state solution.

Company About Us:
En Vogue Events is a full service event planning and design firm with a specific mission to redefine the events industry.  

Recognized and awarded by the business community and our own industry time and again, our team is proven to be resourceful and skilled to ensure your event is managed effectively and efficiently.  The certified event professionals that make up the En Vogue Events team have the same goal for every event, and that is for the return on your investment to be evident and at its maximum. 

Events are another branch of your marketing plan, working alongside your advertising and public relations.  En Vogue Events takes all the measures necessary to create an effective event meeting your needs and goals.  We meet with you and listen to what your goals, needs and wants are. We want to know the message of your event so we can integrate it throughout. make it a point to get to know each individual client so that we can create an out of this world planning experience from beginning to end.  Whether it is a message to employees, to gain press or even to simply celebrate a milestone, En Vogue Events will map out the event to best fit your needs.  We use our passion for the events industry, as well as our experience and knowledge, to create an event that exceeds all expectations across multiple levels.
Experts in creating innovative ideas for events and weddings, our team is ready to amaze you beyond expectation of what events can do... While still able to call for military accuracy planned with absolute detail.

Some of the services we offer:
Event Management
Event Design
Coordination
Concept & Theme
Contract Negotiations
Project Plan & Timeline 
Budget Analysis
Event Logistics
Vendor Management     
Production Schedule
